      "content": "magnesium? i dont think that's gonna touch this feeling. i'm really worried about the money too... honestly i kinda feel like if i can just calm my heart rate down with something, the chest pressure will go away on its own. do you think the magnesium is enough to actually help if i take a higher dose? like maybe 400mg or 600mg at once? i just want to feel normal again so i can sleep.",
